# NoProc — Apple-Grade UI Overhaul · Walkthrough

## What Changed

### 🎨 Design System ([variables.css](file:///C:/Users/admin/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/noproc/css/variables.css))
- **Apple-inspired typography** with SF Pro fallback stack
- **Spring physics** easing curves (`cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1)`) for all transitions
- **6 curated gradient presets**: Aurora, Sunset, Ocean, Midnight, Nature, Rose
- New tokens: `--glass-inner-glow`, `--text-tertiary`, `--bg-elevated`

### 🖼️ Settings Panel ([settings.js](file:///C:/Users/admin/OneDrive/Documents/.Caesar%20Codess%21/NoProc/js/settings.js) + [settings.css](file:///C:/Users/admin/OneDrive/Documents/.Caesar%20Codess%21/NoProc/css/settings.css))
- Full-screen glass overlay accessible from sidebar gear icon
- **Gradient picker**: 6 live-preview swatches with active state
- **Custom wallpaper upload**: File picker → base64 → localStorage persistence
- **Google Sign-In**: Uses Google Identity Services (GIS) OAuth
  - Personalized greeting: "Good Morning, **Caesar**" with gradient text
  - Avatar appears in sidebar footer
  - Account section in settings with sign-out button

### 🎵 Platform-Specific Music
- **Desktop (>900px)**: Extension bridge controls active, Spotify login hidden
- **Mobile (≤900px)**: Spotify miniplayer with bottom bar, extension hidden
- Body classes `is-mobile` / `is-desktop` set dynamically

### 🏗️ Layout ([layout.css](file:///C:/Users/admin/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/noproc/css/layout.css))
- Wallpaper background layer with automatic dark overlay
- **Continuous corner** radius system (Apple-style)
- Responsive breakpoints: desktop → tablet (72px sidebar) → mobile (no sidebar)
- User avatar styling in sidebar footer

### ✨ Components ([components.css](file:///C:/Users/admin/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/noproc/css/components.css))
- **Bloom buttons**: Gradient fills with hover glow overlay
- **Glow timer**: SVG linearGradient stroke with `drop-shadow`
- **Pill-style** timer mode selector
- Platform-aware miniplayer (vertical pill desktop / horizontal bar mobile)

### 🎬 Animations ([animations.css](file:///C:/Users/admin/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/noproc/css/animations.css))
- `blurIn` / `blurOut` page transitions with scale
- Enhanced `blobFloat` with rotation
- `shimmer` keyframes for card loading states
- `settingsIn` / `settingsCardIn` for overlay entrance
- `colonBlink` for clock colon animation

